creator: SpartanNash
descriptionHtml: With the Family Fare Pharmacy app you can manage your prescriptions, request refills, refill by scanning your label, track refill status, find nearby stores to place a refill request and setup dosage reminders to make sure you never forget to take your medications. Bookmark your favorite stores, get driving directions to our pharmacies and manage important appointments.
descriptionShort: Manage prescriptions, request refills, find nearby stores, and more.
